⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Malenia, Blade of Miquella
node ER · ER · ⟦Malenia, Blade of Miquella:ER:557c32⟧

WHO   — Malenia, Blade of Miquella — the undefeated swordswoman who contains the Rot
WHAT  — Miquella's twin, born with the Scarlet Rot sealed inside her body, which has taken an arm, a leg, and more across her life.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the Haligtree, at whose root she stands guard  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Her draw with Radahn at Aeonia, where she first bloomed, scarred Caelid forever; her fall blooms her a second time, as the Goddess of Rot.
HOW   — Fights with a prosthetic blade-arm in the style of the blind swordsman who once sealed an Outer God — and has never known defeat.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  She has never known defeat — only the slow blooming of the thing she carries.

